name: The two creators of chaos
description: The creation of cryptocurrencies was one of the greatest innovations of mankind Bitcoin started it all but it was only the beginning, With the creation of smart contracts, Dapps, Defi and NFTs the imagination has no limits, just as it was in breaking bad the genius behind everything "Bitcoin"(walter) pushed for the need of a better and decentralized monetary system but needed the help of the young Ethereum (jessi) and so everything began to gain strength and changed the world for good.
